Lakewood.El Dorado South, Long Beach, California:
El Dorado Park South is a neighborhood located on the east side of Long Beach. It is a quiet residential neighborhood close to El Dorado Regional Park, the 605 and 405 Freeways and plenty of local shopping. The neighborhood of El Dorado Park South is very close to the Seal Beach City line and is on the Orange and Los Angeles County Line


== Characteristics ==
El Dorado Park South is known for its family oriented atmosphere.
